Mercury in their cup.

01:02:43.282 --> 01:02:44.284
Come on.

01:02:45.186 --> 01:02:46.418
All right!

01:02:47.655 --> 01:02:49.220
My darlings...

01:02:49.222 --> 01:02:51.057
