01:03:00.701 --> 01:03:04.403
Whoo!

01:03:04.405 --> 01:03:07.208
<i>Senor,</i> where's
my marching powder?

01:03:31.197 --> 01:03:32.798
You've got a set of balls.

01:03:32.800 --> 01:03:35.833
Go fetch me
a drink and find out.

01:03:35.835 --> 01:03:37.135
